{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_01_05",
  "title": "IIIX 01 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、話というのは一体何かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what is it you wanted to talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXのデビューが\n来月に決まったと聞きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that IIIX's debut\nhas been set for next month.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "endTime": 8.3545125325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、マネージャーからもう話がいったようだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it seems your manager has already told you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5333333333,
      "endTime": 12.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……その日程、もう少し先には出来ませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is there any way to push that date back?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "endTime": 16.580408080399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん無理を申し上げているのは重々承知です\nただ、グループを組んでまだ日も浅いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand this is a difficult request.\nbut we've only been a group for a short time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8,
      "endTime": 23.9202040196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンも足りているとは言えませんし……\nグループ内で息を合わせる訓練も出来ていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I can't say we've had enough practice…\nWe haven't had enough time to practice together as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "endTime": 30.6814350582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ⅢXが重要なプロジェクトだとは知っています\nだからこそ、万全を期して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know IIIX is an important project.\nThat's why I want to make sure we're fully prepared…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8666666667,
      "endTime": 37.3964848042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan003.m4a",
      "text": "トレーナーからは「ダンスも歌も水準に達している」と\n聞いてるんだけどねえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the trainer told me your dancing and singing\nare excellent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6,
      "endTime": 43.9333333605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "一見すれば、そう見えるかもしれません\nでもライブは一発勝負ですし、入念な準備が必要です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might seem that way at first glance‚\nbut a live performance is a one-shot deal‚ and we need to be thoroughly prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1333333333,
      "endTime": 51.7265299639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan004.m4a",
      "text": "経験者の君がステージに妥協出来ないのは分かる\nだが、これはもう決まったことなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand you can't compromise when it comes to the stage‚ miho-san‚ since you have experience‚\nbut this is already decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9,
      "endTime": 59.2199999571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan005.m4a",
      "text": "会場を押さえて、関係者向けのプレスも既に出した\n私にも、もう予定の変更は不可能だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've already booked the venue and sent out press releases to the media.\nI can't change the schedule now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "endTime": 67.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "endTime": 68.9666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-prekan006.m4a",
      "text": "準備期間は残り少ないけど、頑張ってほしい\n君達ならきちんと仕上げてくれると信じているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's not much time left to prepare‚ but I want you to give it your all.\nI believe you three can make it work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8666666667,
      "endTime": 77.6800000599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9666666667,
      "endTime": 79.19471654889999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "（……ダメだ。私に出来ることはもう、何もない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…It's no use. There's nothing more I can do.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7333333333,
      "endTime": 85.85546496709999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ……\n……とうとう、この日が来てしまったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah…\n…This day has finally come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1,
      "endTime": 93.2082759159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～ん、ふ～ん\n今まで可愛い衣装多かったからな～、新機軸って感じ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ hmm.\nI've worn a lot of cute outfits before‚ this is something new~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4,
      "endTime": 100.5015183295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "特に、kanaだけ真っ白っていうのが一番いいよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially since Kana is the only one in all white! That's the best part!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "endTime": 105.8480272293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、どうどう、kanaイケてない？\nkanaが一番目立っちゃうって思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ how do I look? Isn't Kana cool?\nDon't you think I'll stand out the most?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "endTime": 113.0333334683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "……デザインチェックも仮縫いも一緒にやったじゃない\n今更、見せつけなくても結構よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We already did the design check and the fitting together.\nYou don't have to show off now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3333333333,
      "endTime": 119.65090606160001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん……でも、縫製もちゃんとしてるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… but the sewing is well done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8666666667,
      "endTime": 124.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "さすが『プレタポルテ』ってところかしらね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8,
      "endTime": 128.1406575203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "（最初にデビューした時は）\n（キラキラした衣装が、あんなに眩しかったのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When we debuted‚)\n(those sparkly costumes seemed so dazzling.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3666666667,
      "endTime": 134.0812233396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_05-fyou001.m4a",
      "text": "――ねえ、美帆ちゃん\n私達、なんだか魔法少女に変身したみたいじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hey‚ Miho-chan.\nDon't we look like we've transformed into magical girls?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3,
